1. There are two groups being compared: Group B (NEOMEM-treated) and Group A (CAF-treated).
2. Group B was treated with CAF + Type I collagen membrane (NEOMEM).
3. Group A was treated with CAF.
4. The baseline gingival recession in Group B was 2.34 mm.
5. The standard deviation of the baseline gingival recession in Group B was 0.48 mm.
6. The baseline gingival recession in Group A was 2.52 mm.
7. The standard deviation of the baseline gingival recession in Group A was 0.84 mm.
